# Supervisor
# Mask management ORASTA2 

$_AFF
If GIMPORT
 Gosub AFF From GSAISIE
Else
 If GMESSAGE <>""
  Gosub ERR From GSAISIE
 Else
  Raz GERR , GZNUM
 Endif
Endif
Return

$HORODAT
Local Date    A_DATE
Local Char    A_HEURE(10) , A_USER(10)
Local Char    A_STAMP(15)
A_DATE  = [28/08/2018]
A_HEURE = "00:06:26"
A_USER  = "ADMIN"
A_STAMP = "20180828000626"
Return

$TITRES
Return

$CHG_FMT
Case zoncou
 When "NBINDEX"
  If [M]NBINDEX=0
  Endif
Endcase
Return

$VISU
Local Integer A_REPONSE
Global Integer GPRE_VIEW
If dim(A_WINDPREV)<=0 : Local Char A_WINDPREV(30) : Endif
Local Mask ORASTA2 [STA2]
Gosub HORODAT
Local Inpbox "ORASTA2" From GFONCTION At A_STAMP With A_WINDPREV Mask [STA2] As [SIM_]
Grizo [STA2]5
Boxact [SIM_]
Gosub TITRES
Boxinp [SIM_] Using A_REPONSE
Close Local Inpbox [SIM_]
Close Local Mask [STA2]
Kill GPRE_VIEW
Return

$HARDCOP
Local Integer X1(0..14),X2(0..14),Y1(0..14),Y2(0..14)
X1(0)=1 : X2(0)=112 : Y1(0)=1 : Y2(0)=22
Return

$ON_NBINDEX
Onevent BEFORE_INPUT Call AS_NBINDEX From W1ORASTA2
Return

Subprog AS_NBINDEX
Local Decimal BASPAG
Local Integer INDIC : INDIC = indice
Raz mkstat
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUT1) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(16134,GBOUT2) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(29254,GBOUT3) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(29255,GBOUT4) From OBJDIV
Call TEXTE(29256,GBOUT5) From OBJDIV
## Action STD
Call AS_NBINDEX From ORASTA
Onkey 129 Titled GBOUT1 Call B1_NBINDEX From W1ORASTA2
Onkey 130 Titled GBOUT2 Call B2_NBINDEX From W1ORASTA2
Onkey 131 Titled GBOUT3 Call B3_NBINDEX From W1ORASTA2
Onkey 132 Titled GBOUT4 Call B4_NBINDEX From W1ORASTA2
Onkey 133 Titled GBOUT5 Call B5_NBINDEX From W1ORASTA2
Gosub _AFF
End

Subprog B1_NBINDEX
Local Decimal BASPAG
If !GWEBSERV
 ## Action STD
 Call B1_NBINDEX From ORASTA
Endif
If mkstat=99 : mkstat = 0 : Elsif mkstat=0 : mkstat = 2 : Endif
Gosub _AFF
End

